tasks.title: General Information
tasks.description:
Autocompleted quests: Unlock areas (Corsair curse, prist in peril, children of the sun, etc)
Other Info: ZMI = Disabled ‖ Pest control/Soul wars XP = Disabled ‖ Soul Wars for imbue items (Black Mask)
Shops = Unlimited stocks ‖ Lesser Demon might have a antigrefing mechanic
Start Bonuses: Base XP Multiplier = +400% (or x5) ‖ Drop Rate = x8 ‖ Minigame Points = x8
Farming Tickrate = x5 ‖ Slayer Points = x5 ‖ Dramen Staff (Fairy Rings)
Fairy Rings: Valamore (Stonemason): AJP ‖ Auburn (Crab): AIS ‖ Chasm of Fire: DJR

tasks.title: Grid Master Tiles
tasks.description: All 49 Grid Master Tile Tasks

tasks.title: Complete the Grid Master Tutorial.
tasks.description: Row 4, Task 4 - You will be able to choose all three relics, so since Mine Gold Ore & Chop Maple Logs tasks let you pick another gathering tool it is recommanded to pick the following order: Lumberjack, Power Miner & Animal Wrangler.

tasks.title: Witness the Gemstone Crab burrow away.
tasks.description:
Row 5, Task 5. Quest to get there is autocompleted:
1. Minigame TP to Castle Wars and fairy ring to AIS and skip to step 4 or Travel with Regulus Cento east of Varrock
2. Run or take the bird if possible to Quetzacalli
3. Follow Mountain Guide close to the bridge to get to Nemus Retreat.
4. Run south to the Rowboat and take it to Kastori
5. Run north to the Gemstone Crab if you do not see it enter the Passage to Gemstone Crab.
tasks.reward: Gatherer: You gain the Gatherer benefit. You select three Gathering or Support skills, then whenever you gain XP in one of your 3 selected Gathering or Support skills, you'll gain 50% of that XP in the other 2 selected skills. Available skills are: Mining, Fishing, Woodcutting, Hunter, Agility, Slayer and Thieving.

tasks.title: Chop maple logs.
tasks.description: Row 3, Col 4 - 45 Woodcutting

tasks.title: Mine gold ore.
tasks.description: Row 5, Col 4 - 40 Mining

tasks.title: Subdue Tempoross.
tasks.description: Row 5, Col 3 - 35 Fishing
tasks.reward: Craftsman: You gain the Craftsman benefit. You select three Artisan skills, then whenever you gain XP in one of your 3 selected Craftsman skills, you'll gain 50% of that XP in the other 2 selected skills. Available skills are: Construction, Cooking, Crafting, Firemaking, Fletching, Herblore, Runecraft and Smithing.

tasks.title: Kill Ogress
tasks.description:
Row 1, Col 4 - Quest to get here is autocompleted. Can be safespotted and killed with Magic
FYI: If picking prayer you can level two other skills with prayer, since prayer is free with Golden God Relic.
tasks.reward: You gain the Combtant benefit. You select three Combat skills, then whenever you gain XP in one of your 3 selected Combat skills, you'll gain 50% of that XP in the other 2 selected skills. Available skills are: Attack, Strength, Defence, Hitpoints, Ranged, Magic and Prayer.

tasks.title: Gain over 30,000 coins from one Alchemy spell.
tasks.description: Row 4, Col 1 - This can be done when creating unlimited cash stack with Golden God at Stonemason or Buy Rune Platelegs Scavvo's Rune Store in Champions' Guild for 64k to High Alch with 55 Magic or Buy Tall box hedge from Garden supplier in Falador Park for 100k to Low Alch 21 Magic
tasks.reward: Production Prodigy: When doing the following activities, all items are processed at once: Smelting ores, Smithing bars (does not work with the Superheat item spell) and making Cannonballs Fletching logs, stringing Bows and cutting bolt tips Making headless arrows, regular arrows, bolts, darts, and javelins (capped at 10x the regular amount per action.) Cleaning herbs and making Potions which do no have a stackable secondary ingredient. Cooking food and making Jugs of Wine. Crafting leather, uncut gems, glassblowing, jewellery pottery, Battlestaves and spinning flax or wool. Full XP is given for items processed using this relic. There is a 25% chance that you will make an extra product, which will be sent to your Bank if you have space. The additional product will also grant XP. Additionally Crafting, Smithing, Herblore, Fletching and Cooking are boosted by +12.

tasks.title: Open Bryophyta's Chest.
tasks.description: Row 6, Col 4 - You need a key to be able to enter and complete this tile. This can be done early since we have 8x droprate.
tasks.reward: Combat Masteries: All Combat Masteries increase by 1 tier. Melee I: Melee hits have a 25% chance to roll damage twice and take the highest result. Ranged I: Damage rolls beneath 30% of max hit with Ranged are increased to 30%. Magic I: When you roll above 90% of your max hit with Magic, damage is increased by 50%. Passive: 95% chance to save weapon charges, ammunition, and runes used for spells.

tasks.title: Reach a total skill level of 500.
tasks.description: Row 2, Col 4 - Take advantage of Gatherer (Gemstone Crab), Craftsman (Tempoross) & Combatant (Ogress) tiles to get levels in multiple skills.
tasks.reward: XP Lamp: An experience lamp containing 25,000 XP to be used on any skill.

tasks.title: Defeat the Lesser Demon in the Wizards Tower
tasks.description: Row 7, Col 4 - Need Magic or Ranged
tasks.reward: Minimum Potential: You gain the Minimum Potential perk. Your Melee, Ranged & Magic hits will never deal below 5 damage. You can still miss your attacks.

tasks.title: Obtain some Valuables from a house in Varlamore.
tasks.description: Row 3, Col 1 - 50 Thieving, Steal key from Wealthy citizen at Bazaar and go into one of the 3 houses that is empty to steal valuables, you might have to turn them into Oriana.
tasks.reward: Golden God: You gain the following perks to the High and Low Alchemy spells: The spells have no rune cost or level requirement. Items give 15% more gold, and have a 65% chance to not be consumed. When cast on a stack of items, the spells will automatically be recast over time, until the stack is depleted or moved. You gain the following perks to Prayer: 20,000 Coins can be offered at Prayer altars in exchange for Prayer XP equivalent to using a dragon bone. This respects altar XP modifiers. Normal altars have no modifiers. All items purchased from some select shops can be noted, provided the item can be noted at all. There will be a new button on select shops which toggles this effect.

tasks.title: Cook a shark while wearing a Chef's hat.
tasks.description: Row 2, Col 5 - Chief's Hat: Goblin, Imp or Shayzien Style Shop (Fairy ring DJR) and 80 Cooking. You should have unlocked Production Prodigy & Golden God Relic before training cooking, then you buy fish noted from Frankie fishing shop in Port Piscarilius (Take the boat from Port Sarim or fairy ring: AKR), then cook it in a place like Rogues Den.
tasks.reward: Corrupted Shark: A Shark that isn't consumed when eaten. Heals a base of 20 hitpoints.

tasks.title: Defeat Jal-Zek within the Inferno.
tasks.description: Row 1, Col 5 - Wave 35 in the Inferno, require completion of Fight Caves. Recommanded to complete Open Bryophyta's chest. to unlock the first Combat Masteries.
tasks.reward: Slayer Master: Always be on-task for all slayer monsters and unlock all slayer task perks for free.

tasks.title: Build a Demonic Throne in your Player Owned House.
tasks.description:
Row 7, Col 2 - You want to unlock Golden God with a good cash stack and unlock some XP multipliers, Hire a servant (20-50 Con) in Ardy Buy Marble Block from stonemason.
Level 1-63 use XP lamp from Reach 500 total level or use planks and Limestone brick(Lvl 5), Marble fireplace 63-72, Marble portal Nexus 72-79, Marble wall 79-99 or 79-95 Crystal throne 95-99 (Magic stones).
tasks.reward: Thunder Kopesh: A powerful Khopesh, imbued with the power of thunder and lightning. Deals full damage to the Corporeal Beast Has a 20% chance to trigger a AoE lightning bolt under the target, hitting anything in a 1 tile radius, which rolls with 50% of the original attacks max hit. Special Attack - 50% Attacks twice. If either attack is successful an additional lightning bolt is summoned rolling up to 100% of the original attacks max hit. Attack Bonuses Stab: + 65 Slash: + 110 Other Stats Melee Str: + 100 Attack Speed: 4 ticks Attack Range: 1 tile

tasks.title: Obtain a rare unique from Tombs of Amascut.
tasks.description: Row 7, Col 1 - Recommanded to complete Build a Demonic Throne for the Thunder Khopesh melee weapon.
tasks.reward: Mega Rare Scroll: You gain the Mega Rare Scroll. Choose one of the three mega rares from raids: Scythe of Vitur, Tumeken's Shadow or Twisted Bow.

tasks.title: Complete the Inferno in 30 minutes or less.
tasks.description: Row 1, Col 7 - Aoe damage is important here, unlocking Sunlight spear and Sunlit bracers from the column 6 will be a huge help for this task.
tasks.reward: Guardian: This item will allow you to summon a powerful Guardian Thrall, lasting 30 minutes The guardian will attack your target with whatever style it is weak to. When you are in multi-combat it will cast an AoE attack if the target is weak to range or magic. The Guardian's stats are: Min hit: 5 Max hit: 13 Attack Speed: 4 The Guardian does not work in PvP. This perk will also work inside The Gauntlet.

tasks.title: Defeat all 4 Awakened bosses.
tasks.description: Row 6, Col 1 - Good luck you are on your own on this one!
tasks.reward: Battlehat: A tribrid helmet with no negative bonuses, that also functions as a slayer helm. Attack Bonuses Stab: + 15 Slash: + 15 Crush: + 15 Magic: + 15 Range: + 15 Defence Bonuses Stab: + 60 Slash: + 60 Crush: + 60 Magic: + 60 Range: + 60 Other Stats Melee Str: + 10 Range Str: + 5 Magic Str: + 5% Prayer: + 10

tasks.title: Complete all tasks in column 4.
tasks.reward: Increase XP gain by 200% for all skills.
